pull_request.title: Size reduction
pull_request.body:
- Image sizes reduced for httpd (>4GB to 296MB) and nginx (>3GB to 77MB)
- Documentation split between README (built) and USAGE (also at docker hub: https://hub.docker.com/u/openquantumsafe)
- Configuration options extended and documented
- Tests updated
- (non-portable) Optimised variant only build for curl and tagged ':optimised' (same docker hub location)
- generic/portable version tagged ':latest'

CCI tests ran OK at: https://circleci.com/gh/baentsch/oqs-software/107

pull_request.title: Change hybrid curve numbers to use private range as recommended in Internet-Draft
pull_request.body:
Fixes #168. 

https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-tls-hybrid-design-00 says the code points reserved for hybrid private use are `0x2F00..0x2FFF`, so this updates to use that range.  

Also changes a few recently added non-hybrid curve numbers to be sequential.

Numbers recorded in https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/12YarzaNv3XQNLnvDsWLlRKwtZFhRrDdWf36YlzwrPeg/edit?usp=sharing
